OL,4,CWorld's biggest coal company bets on
OL,5,Csolar power
OL,6, The world's largest coal mining firm is
OL,7, to "aggressively" pursue solar energy
OL,8, and continue to close smaller mines.
OL,10,FCoal India Limited (CIL) plans to
OL,11,Finvest in a 3,000 megawatt solar energy
OL,12,Fproject in a joint venture with
OL,13,Fstate-run NLC India.
OL,15,FThe company also wants to compete in
OL,16,FIndia's solar auctions and win projects
OL,17,Fby offering the lowest prices for clean
OL,18,Fpower.
OL,20,FIt marks a major shift for the firm,
OL,21,Fwhich produces most of India's coal.
